<% content_for :title, "Privacy policy" %>

<div class="mt-4">
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Privacy policy</h1>
  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400">Last updated: March 14, 2026</p>

  <div class="mt-6 space-y-6 text-stone-700 dark:text-stone-300">
    <p>Beervana ("the App") is operated by Joe Masilotti. This policy describes what data we collect, how we use it, and your choices.</p>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">Data we collect</h2>

      <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">Account information</h3>
          <p class="mt-1">When you sign in with Apple, we receive your name and email address (or a private relay address if you choose to hide your email). We use this to identify your account.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">Usage data</h3>
          <p class="mt-1">We store the breweries you stamp and bookmark. This data is tied to your account so you can access it across sessions.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">Push notification tokens</h3>
          <p class="mt-1">If you opt in to push notifications, we store your device token to send you notifications. You can disable notifications at any time in your device settings.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">Data we do not collect</h2>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>We do not collect your location.</li>
        <li>We do not use analytics or tracking SDKs.</li>
        <li>We do not sell, share, or rent your data to third parties.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">Data storage</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">Your data is stored on servers hosted by Fly.io in the United States. We use encryption in transit (HTTPS) to protect your data.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">Third-party services</h2>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Apple Sign-In:</strong> authentication is handled by Apple. See <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/" class="underline">Apple's privacy policy</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Brewery data:</strong> initial brewery information comes from <a href="https://www.openbrewerydb.org/" class="underline">Open Brewery DB</a> (open source, MIT license).</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">Data retention and deletion</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">Your data is retained as long as your account exists. To request deletion of your account and all associated data, email <a href="mailto:joe@masilotti.com" class="underline">joe@masilotti.com</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">Children's privacy</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">The App is not directed at children under 21. We do not knowingly collect data from anyone under 21.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">We may update this policy from time to time. We will notify you of significant changes through the App or by email.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">Contact</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">Questions about this policy? Email <a href="mailto:joe@masilotti.com" class="underline">joe@masilotti.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
